  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  men and women

          -  aged from 18 to 65 years

          -  paraplegia Th2-Th12

          -  spinal cord injury had occurred &gt;12 weeks ago

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  infections

          -  fever

          -  diabetes

          -  heart failure stadium III

          -  renal insufficiency stadium III.

          -  scars, wounds or other injuries in the area of treatment

          -  skin type V and VI on Fitzpatrick scale
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
